//=========================================================================
//  Changes the pointer at the specified position in this list.
//=========================================================================
//  Parameters:
//   i_pList       - Basing pointer of the list returned by BasicList_new().
//   i_index       - Position of the element.
//   i_pointer     - The pointer that is changed.
